    <div class="main review-item" id="8544108">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8544108/" class="title-link">让一个老外帮我们寻找失落的记忆，怪丢人的</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8544108"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/RiverPheonix/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1205892-9.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/RiverPheonix/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">为人帅表</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2017-05-16"
      class="main-meta">2017-05-16 14:47:10</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8544108_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  一          在一个地方生活和旅游完全是两个概念。旅游的人，花着钱占着时间，所以必须要仔细感受，希望在这仅有的时间里深切地了解他所行走的目的地，所以他对所见所闻都印象深刻。然而也是因为时间上的局限性，旅行的人对于一座城市的认识往往充满了偶然，这种偶然又会被旅...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_8544108_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_8544108_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










